13.0 Legal assistance
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
Insurance sum payable: DKK 150,000 per person.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
13.1 Coverage
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance covers the insured's expenses for legal
assistance, including case costs, in the event that the
insured, as a private person, through inadvertence and without
a contractual relationship, causes injury to a third party or
involuntarily breaks local laws or public regulations and thus
incurs compensation liability under civil law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
13.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
Privatsikring undertakes to pay up to DKK 150,000 for legal
assistance, including case costs, in the event that the insured, on
account of injury or damage, is sued on the basis of civil law.
.sp 3mm
In addition, the insurance covers the participation by the insured in
civil or criminal legal proceedings abroad, in cases where the
hearing cannot be held in Denmark. The insurance covers necessary
expenses for hotel accommodation and transport (maximum: air
travel/economy class). Payment is conditional upon:
.of 5mm
*¤the insured being called to a hearing as a party to the proceedings
or as a witness
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤the insured, in the opinion of Privatsikring, having a legal interest in
appearing
.of
.of 5mm
*¤the expenses not being covered by another party.
.sp 3mm
the victim of an assault. Payment of compensation is dependent on the
insured reporting the assault to the police.
