:FED.
15.2 Compensation
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The insurance coverage amounts to up to DKK 500,000 per person. The
compensation payable is calculated according to the sum a perpetrator
deemed liable would be required to pay for similar actions under
Danish law.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
